(1711, 'Glamor of Fire', 55, 5, NULL, 'Baratheon only. Any Phase : choose and kill a character you control (cannot be saved) to choose and put into play a character in your dead pile that was killed this phase.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'narrow107.jpg'),
(1712, 'Sacrificed to Two Gods', 55, 5, NULL, 'Greyjoy only. Response : after a challenge resolves in which a character did not count its STR because of intimidate, kill that character. Response : save a holy character from being killed. Then, that character claims one power.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'narrow109.jpg'),
(1713, 'Outfitted for War', 55, 4, 1, 'Greyjoy only. Attach to a Warship location you control. Attached location is immune to non-plot card effects. Add three to your total STR during any military challenge in which you control at least one attacking character.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'narrow108.jpg'),
(1714, 'The Brazen Beasts', 55, 1, 4, 'Renown. Response : after an opponent''s character''s STR is reduced to zero, The Brazen Beasts claim one power. (Limit once per phase.)', NULL, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, 'narrow115.jpg'),
(1715, 'Meereenese Fighting Pit', 55, 2, 1, 'Challenges : kneel Meereenese Fighting Pit to choose and stand a Dragon character or a character with one or more Weapon attachments.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'narrow116.jpg'),
(1716, 'Dragonbone Bow', 55, 4, 1, 'Attached character gains deadly. Challenges : kneel attached character to have it participate as an attacker in the current challenge.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'narrow117.jpg'),
(1717, 'Lead by Example', 55, 6, NULL, 'Players must declare two or more characters to attack or defend in a challenge.', 3, NULL, 4, NULL, 1, 'narrow120.jpg'),
(1718, 'Flood Waters', 55, 5, NULL, 'Any Phase : kneel two influence or kneel one Warship location to choose a River plot card in any player''s used plot pile. Trigger that plot''s ''When revealed'' effect as if you had just revealed it.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'narrow110.jpg'),
(1719, 'Little and Less', 55, 5, NULL, 'You may play this card during any response window. Response : until the end of the phase, players cannot play any additional responses. (Cannot be canceled.)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'narrow118.jpg'),
(1720, 'House of Dreams', 55, 3, NULL, 'After you announce House of Dreams as your Agenda, choose from your deck a unique, in-House, non-limited location. That location starts the game in play and gains the text : ''Immune to opponents'' non-plot card effects.'' Draw six cards for your setup hand. You cannot spend more than three gold during setup.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'narrow119.jpg'),
(1721, 'The Second Sons', 55, 1, 7, 'Stealth. No attachments. Lower the cost to play The Second Sons by one for each unique Lannister or Targaryen character you control. Response : after a player draws a card through a card effect during the challenges phase, choose a character. That character gets -1 STR until the end of the phase.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 7, NULL, 'narrow105.jpg'),
(1722, 'Rhymes with Meek', 55, 5, NULL, 'Response : kneel one influence to save a unique Stark or Greyjoy character from being killed. Then, attach Rhymes with Meek to the saved character (counts as a Condition attachment with the text ''Attached character cannot have its STR raised or lowered by card effects.'')', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'narrow103.jpg');
